00:24:43.539 --> 00:24:47.156
iz, zenen zey geven o- BEFORE,

00:24:47.156 --> 00:24:49.558
hob ikh zey aroysgenumen fun dort.

00:24:49.749 --> 00:24:52.275
vayl di kinder hobn zeyer nisht gut gehat.

00:24:52.719 --> 00:24:56.611
