00:24:56.702 --> 00:24:59.492
hot nakher vi ikh hob gezen di bet,

00:24:59.503 --> 00:25:01.677
hot zi yede vokh geganen,

00:25:01.677 --> 00:25:05.196
zi hot genumen dos ibertsik un zi hot es gevashn,

00:25:05.207 --> 00:25:07.060
un me hot es geprest,

00:25:07.060 --> 00:25:11.136
un zi hot yede vokh ibergetsoygn. BUT nakher

00:25:11.147 --> 00:25:12.761
iz gevezn

00:25:13.425 --> 00:25:15.563
vi di doytshn,

00:25:15.973 --> 00:25:19.410
di ale ofitsirn, ikh hob fargesn der gas,

00:25:19.517 --> 00:25:21.666
vos a bombe iz arayngefaln,

00:25:21.666 --> 00:25:25.147
un me hot derharget ale kinder. ir hot gehert derfun?

00:25:26.233 --> 00:25:28.466
dortn iz geven,

00:25:28.466 --> 00:25:31.555
zenen di doytshn, di groyser makhtn,

00:25:31.555 --> 00:25:34.550
hobn dortn gehat zeyere OFFICES.

00:25:34.552 --> 00:25:36.946
un dortn iz gevezn a froy

00:25:36.946 --> 00:25:39.660
UNK hot es geheysn.

00:25:39.767 --> 00:25:40.979
a gro- a

00:25:40.979 --> 00:25:43.238
a vikhtike PLACE.

00:25:43.378 --> 00:25:46.984
hob ikh dortn arayngegebn di beyde kinder.

00:25:47.765 --> 00:25:49.261
az

00:25:50.043 --> 00:25:51.691
Hitler iz avek,

00:25:52.963 --> 00:25:54.935
iz mayn man ahin geganen,

00:25:54.935 --> 00:25:56.766
er geyt nemen di kinder.

00:25:56.777 --> 00:25:59.336
bald di zelbe tsayt.

00:25:59.510 --> 00:26:01.862
zog ikh, Simon, nem nisht di kinder,

00:26:01.907 --> 00:26:03.187
ikh hob gornisht

00:26:03.223 --> 00:26:05.195
nisht ayntsuheytsn,

00:26:05.231 --> 00:26:07.219
ikh hob nisht vu tsu trikenen,

00:26:07.219 --> 00:26:09.714
ikh hob nisht keyn MAID, ikh bin aleyn.

00:26:10.563 --> 00:26:13.190
hot er gornisht gezogt mir, er iz avekgeganen.

00:26:13.247 --> 00:26:15.368
er iz tsurikgekumen mit di kinder.

00:26:16.183 --> 00:26:19.822
un bay der nakht is dortn arayn a UNK,

00:26:19.997 --> 00:26:23.535
un er hot ale derharget, afilek di froy fun dem

00:26:24.468 --> 00:26:25.984
in zakhn.

00:26:25.984 --> 00:26:28.546
un haynt iz dortn do

00:26:29.548 --> 00:26:31.883
kinder, se gemakht a,

00:26:31.883 --> 00:26:33.913
a SPECIAL zakh

00:26:35.274 --> 00:26:38.244
az di kinder zenen derharget gevorn un ales,

00:26:38.272 --> 00:26:39.999
iz es dortn do,

00:26:40.044 --> 00:26:42.620
vu, se iz zeyer a vikhtike gas.

00:26:42.980 --> 00:26:45.551
der dokter afilek vo- hot oykhet gevoy-

00:26:45.551 --> 00:26:46.772
gevoynt dort.

00:26:47.385 --> 00:26:49.269
vi hot, UNK,

00:26:50.000 --> 00:26:52.188
UNK hot zi geheysn.

00:26:52.852 --> 00:26:53.836
un er hot bald,

00:26:53.836 --> 00:26:58.393
ven er, ikh vil, er geyt nisht di zelbe nakht ahin,

00:26:58.421 --> 00:27:00.339
volt ikh oykh nisht gehat di kinder.

00:27:01.712 --> 00:27:05.261
vayl mayn's a tante hot dortn gearbet bay ir,

00:27:05.306 --> 00:27:07.832
un zi hot dort gehat tsvey kinder,

00:27:08.259 --> 00:27:11.527
un zenen zey take di kinder umgekumen,

00:27:12.613 --> 00:27:16.826
un zi iz do ahergekumen un zi hot gevoynt in Toronto do,

00:27:17.051 --> 00:27:19.931
un zi hot khasene gehat mit a raykhn man,

00:27:20.645 --> 00:27:26.275
BUT veyst zi iz gevezn nervez UNK,

00:27:27.395 --> 00:27:31.726
un se gekumen tsun ir a galekh, hot er dertseylt dos alesding,

00:27:32.424 --> 00:27:37.768
un azoy iz gevezn. tsu dertseyln, hert oys,

00:27:38.145 --> 00:27:41.649
ken men dertseyln fun mitsriyas mitsrayim.

00:27:42.718 --> 00:27:46.661
vos meynt ir az ikh dertseyl azoy, se iz azoy poshet?

00:27:48.641 --> 00:27:52.854
un ikh bin nokh geganen un ikh hob nokh ales erleydikt.

00:27:53.012 --> 00:27:57.276
vegn mayn man iz nisht geganen fun fun danet biz danet.

00:27:57.602 --> 00:28:01.629
azoy ikh hob im avekgezetst, azoy iz er gezitsn,

00:28:01.753 --> 00:28:06.492
der MOLEMANS hot im oysgeleyent shpiln UNK,

00:28:06.495 --> 00:28:09.442
ir veyst vos UNK? epes in gortn.

00:28:09.836 --> 00:28:12.885
un er iz nor gezitsn mit MOLEMANS

00:28:13.987 --> 00:28:19.578
un MOLEMANS hot undz zeyer gern gehat, zey hobn zeyer a sakh getuen.

00:28:19.590 --> 00:28:23.308
dos heyst keyn gelt khas-vekholile hobn zey undz nisht gegebn,

00:28:23.336 --> 00:28:25.316
nor gebrengt fleysh,

00:28:25.316 --> 00:28:27.245
gekokht tsuzamen,

00:28:27.487 --> 00:28:29.290
gehat respekt,

00:28:29.310 --> 00:28:31.650
mer vi di di yidn hobn do,

00:28:32.465 --> 00:28:34.164
nor ikh vel beser zayn do.

00:28:35.418 --> 00:28:37.606
ikh vil aykh fregn,

00:28:37.815 --> 00:28:39.111
ir zent geven

00:28:39.111 --> 00:28:41.538
bay Hilperts in Stoker, yo?

00:28:42.152 --> 00:28:44.216
in K- in Kreynem, in Kreynem.

00:28:42.236 --> 00:28:43.091
in Kreynem.

