dan hob ikh gehat

00:29:00.208 --> 00:29:02.109
bakent a froy,

00:29:02.250 --> 00:29:05.116
a katoylishe, vos hot gehat a gesheft,

00:29:05.152 --> 00:29:10.834
fun BISCUITS, fun broyt, fun di ale zakhn. ze'mir gevorn zeyer bafrayndet,

00:29:10.957 --> 00:29:14.546
un dortn zenen arum geven kinder bahaltn,

00:29:14.703 --> 00:29:16.624
un ven ikh bin geganen,

00:29:16.624 --> 00:29:19.813
ikh hob aykh gezogt, ikh hob mikh umgedreyt un keyner nisht geven.

00:29:19.850 --> 00:29:24.688
un dortn bin ikh geganen yedn tog azoy vi a frumer yid geyt in shul.

00:29:25.098 --> 00:29:26.561
